@startuml
|User|
start
:Clicks the "Forgot password" option;

|System|
:Prepares the password recovery form;

|User|
:Sees the password recovery form on the Login Page;
:Writes the registered email address;
:Clicks the "Recover password" button;

|System|
:Sends a query to verify whether the email exists in the database;

|Database|
:Returns the query;

|System|
:Verifies the email exists in the system;

if (Does the email exist in the system?) then (yes)
    :Generates a password recovery token associated with the User account;
    :Sends a request to the configured email service to deliver the recovery email;

    |Email Service|
    :Processes the recovery email request;

    |System|
    :Receives response from the email service;

    if (Was the request to the email service completed successfully?) then (yes)
        |User|
        :Sees confirmation message on the Login Page indicating that the recovery email has been sent;
        stop
    else (no)
        |User|
        :Sees an error message on the Login Page;
        stop
    endif

else (no)
    |User|
    :Sees an error message on the Login Page indicating that the email is not registered;
    stop
endif
@enduml